uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:01:03.000Z","msg":"班保皇黨又打人又賄選 但對住鏡頭話自己比人搞"},{"pid":"b993daa6f7340f1b062a040bd2c55a6100367f4e","tid":1649011,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:51:55.000Z","msg":"唔止謝sir，連er er er sir都&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4e7fabcf103fe2f53cb80f8175067ec05e371fe8","tid":1649011,"uid":294152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:42:43.000Z","msg":"條仆街係香港會議展覽中心MIS MANAGER, 名： Franko Ng"},{"pid":"b2f93eab8461db1f137f64e19cbcd438e09aaeb7","tid":1649011,"uid":115914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:40:25.000Z","msg":"佢有個女㗎，好似讀女校！"},{"pid":"d09d88d32b6d0800b3d2632c4d2ed9f6804fe892","tid":1649011,"uid":260023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:20:03.000Z","msg":"幫我推一下<br />\n<br />\n一齊實現《五大訴求》《真實雙普選》路線圖 反對《緊急法》入嚟<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651075</a>"},{"pid":"976b84a57c1ebd6ff345d546a3ffda15d57a1acb","tid":1649011,"uid":299119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 我唔識佢. 我唔喺住嗰區, 我唔係嗰區選民. 我只係想香港人多個選擇. 而北角係硬戰場之一, 唔易打, 真係需要支持.<br />\n唔要仆街建制, 唔要老人政治.<br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/483780698831135/posts/536523086890229?sf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F483780698831135%2Fposts%2F536523086890229%3Fsf&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9kBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=11bf490e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/483780698831135/posts/536523086890229?sf</a><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;仇栩欣眾籌經費展開<br />\n<br />\n東區區議會是本港自動當選的重災區之一，位於炮台山的城市花園也不例外。城市花園過往二十年，只得兩次（2007,2011）能夠「有得揀」。我，仇栩欣的目標十分清晰，希望能夠為城市花園帶來具認受性的區議員，務求做到以民為本，依民所願來作社區建設。阿欣今次的選舉經費需要每一位相同理念的有心人作支持，眾籌目標為六萬元。<br />\n<br />\n眾籌捐贈不能超過一千元或以上，否則便須補上全名及住址作申報，而不能提供相關證明的話，有關捐贈便需捐出而不能作選舉用途。<br />\n<br />\n眾籌金額尚欠一半才達標，希望大家能夠支持!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/s/chauhy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fs%2Fchauhy%2F&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9kBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=4057e3a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/s/chauhy/</a><br />\n<br />\n選舉廣告 l 1 l 自家製作&rdquo;"}]}